<topic id='business_definition_midwife_episode.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Midwife Episode - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_midwife_episode">Midwife Episode</xref>
 is an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity_group">ACTIVITY GROUP</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_midwife_episode">Midwife Episode</xref>
 is a continuous period of time a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 uses a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_hospital_bed">Hospital Bed</xref>
 or 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_delivery">Delivery</xref>
 facility as part of a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_hospital_provider_spell">Hospital Provider Spell</xref>
 or 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_care_home_stay__midwife_care_">Care Home Stay (Midwife Care)</xref>, under the direct care of a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_midwife">MIDWIFE</xref>. This may be during a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_maternity_episode">Maternity Episode</xref>
 or 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_labour_and_delivery">Labour and Delivery</xref>
 for the mother but may also be for a baby following a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_registrable_birth">REGISTRABLE BIRTH</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_midwife">MIDWIFE</xref>
 with overall responsibility for a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_midwife_episode">Midwife Episode</xref>
 must be identified. If the responsible 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_midwife">MIDWIFE</xref>
 changes then a new 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_midwife_episode">Midwife Episode</xref>
 or 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_consultant_episode__hospital_provider_">Consultant Episode (Hospital Provider)</xref>
 begins.        </p>
      <p>
General medical care during the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_midwife_episode">Midwife Episode</xref>
 is the responsibility of the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 own 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_general_medical_practitioner">GENERAL MEDICAL PRACTITIONER</xref>
 who is acting as a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_consultant">CONSULTANT</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
